.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, trance, rock, jazz
1. the fan disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan jazz is on the right of the fan trance##1
3. the fan trance is somewhere between the fan disco and the fan rock##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | trance | jazz | rock |

